a) Primary purpose of banner MOTD
MOTD = Message of the Day
Displays a message when a user logs into a device
Used for security warnings / legal notices


b) Packet Tracer benefit & limitation
Benefit:
Safe virtual environment to practice networking without hardware
Limitation:
Does not fully replicate real-world hardware behavior


c) Difference: Static NAT vs Dynamic NAT vs PAT
Feature                	Static NAT                	Dynamic NAT                  	PAT
Mapping               	One-to-one	                Pool-based	               Many-to-one
IP usage                	Fixed                     	Dynamic	                  Shared
Example	           1 public IP per device          	Uses pool	                 Uses ports


d) NAT commands (Cisco Packet Tracer)
Router(config)# ip nat inside source static 192.168.1.2 200.1.1.2
Router(config)# ip nat inside
Router(config)# ip nat outside
Router(config)# access-list 1 permit 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255
Router(config)# ip nat inside source list 1 pool NATPOOL


